dct_title_s: A map of the Holy Land or ye travels of the children of Israel out of Egypt through the Red Sea & the wilderness into Canaan
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "English Miles".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries of the twelve tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
dct_subject_sm: Israelites crossing the Red Sea (Biblical event)
